<?xml version="1.0" encoding="GB2312"?>
<Body>
	<Title>甘肃武威第一幼儿园59名儿童食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007年9月21日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">9月19日上午</Time>，<Location lid="l1">甘肃省武威市第一幼儿园</Location><Participant sid="s1">部分儿童</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>发烧、呕吐、肚子痛等<Object oid="o1">症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e2">经<Participant sid="s2">当地卫生部门</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d2" type="operation">诊断</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3">该幼儿园发生<Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4"><Time tid="t4" type="timeInterval">截至20日上午11时</Time>，该幼儿园的<Participant sid="s4" type="recipient">100多名儿童</Participant>到<Location lid="l4">医院</Location>接受了<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">其中<Participant oid="o5">59名儿童</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="action">确诊</Denoter>为明显中毒</Event>，<Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d5" type="operation">留院治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 
    
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7">记者</Participant>从武威市<Denoter did="d7" type="perception">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，<Event eid="e8"><Time tid="t8" type="relTime">19日上午</Time>，<Location lid="l8">武威市第一幼儿园</Location><Participant sid="s8">个别儿童</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>发烧、呕吐、肚子痛等<Object oid="o8">症状</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>当天下午，有上述症状的孩子明显增多，<Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">幼儿园</Participant>立即向<Participant oid="o9">凉州区卫生局</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="operation">汇报</Denoter>情况</Event>。<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">之后</Time>，<Participant sid="s10" type="agent">幼儿园</Participant>按照上级部门要求<Denoter did="d10" type="statement">通知</Denoter><Participant oid="o10" type="recipient">家长</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">孩子</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>发烧、肚子痛等<Object oid="o11">症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e12">立即带<Participant oid="o12">孩子</Participant>到<Location lid="l12">武威市人民医院儿科</Location><Denoter did="d12" type="operation">检查治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">武威市人民医院</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">启动</Denoter><Object oid="o13">突发事件紧急预案</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e14">并且<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">抽调</Denoter>所有医护人员</Event><Event eid="e15"><Denoter did="d15" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l15" type="destination">儿科</Location></Event></Sentence>。<Sentence><Event eid="e16">对<Object oid="o16">这次大型的突发公共卫生事件救治工作</Object>全部<Denoter did="d16" type="action">垫资</Denoter>，对<Object oid="o16">所有前来检查治疗的儿童</Object>全部实行免费</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>由于担心自己的孩子也出现中毒症状，<Event eid="e17"><Participant oid="o17">有百余名儿童</Participant>陆续在家长的带领下到<Location lid="l17">医院</Location><Denoter did="d17" type="operation">观察治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>到当晚8时，武威市人民医院儿科住院部所有床位满员。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e18">之后来检查的<Participant oid="o18">部分孩子</Participant><Denoter did="d18" type="movement">转院</Denoter>到<Location lid="l18">凉州区人民医院</Location></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>截至<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d19" type="action">发稿</Denoter></Event>时，武威市卫生部门确定<Event eid="e20"><Participant sid="s20">59名儿童</Participant>有明显<Denoter did="d20" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter>症状</Event>，<Event eid="e21">正在<Location lid="l21">医院</Location>接受<Denoter did="d21" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e22">据<Participant sid="s22">凉州区卫生局</Participant><Denoter did="d22" type="action">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e23">发生中毒事件的<Object oid="o23">幼儿园所有餐具</Object>已经<Denoter did="d23" type="operation">封存</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e24">并<Denoter did="d24" type="movement">移交</Denoter><Location lid="l24">武威市疾控中心</Location></Event><Event eid="e25"><Denoter did="d25" type="operation">检验</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
